      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s practically brand new? This car is an absolute gem and honestly looks like it just left the showroom floor! I've taken such good care of it, it's basically flawless inside and out. It drives like a total dream and I'm honestly sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely fall in love with it. It's been babied since day one\u2014come check it out, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in showroom condition. This example features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, equipped with six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that pulls cleanly to an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a limited-slip M Variable Differential Lock. This chassis has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement, rod bearing replacement, and a complete VANOS overhaul. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, providing the telepathic steering response and balanced damping these E46s are celebrated for. A rare find with zero deferred maintenance and impeccable mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
